  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a tava griddle over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and saut\u00105 until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and saut\u00105 for another minute.",
    "Add the black beans, dried apricots, raisins, pistachios, smoked paprika, ground cumin, ground coriander, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the mother sauce base, water, and ghee (if using). Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook, stirring occasionally, until the liquid has reduced and the beans are coated in the spice mixture, about 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the fresh parsley and lemon juice.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired.",
    "Let the tagine rest for 10 minutes before serving to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Serve with rice, naan, or roti, if desired."
  ],
